{"tid":95193,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"係幾年前，我同一個寡婦結左婚。。。。。。。","createTime":"2017-01-26T00:11:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-26T01:46:17.000Z","uid":5812,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"38e7311eaaa67d966389bd73e3606100d34bfd10","tid":95193,"uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T00:11:13.000Z","msg":"係幾年前 <br />\n我同一個寡婦結左婚 <br />\n佢有一個已成年既女 <br />\n後來嫁左比我老豆 <br />\n<br />\n咁我繼女就做左我後媽 <br />\n而我老豆就做左我女婿 <br />\n<br />\n兩年後我老婆同我生左一個仔 <br />\n佢係我後媽既同母異父既細路 <br />\n我個仔叫我「老豆」 <br />\n我就叫我個仔「舅父」 <br />\n<br />\n我繼女又為我老豆生左一個仔 <br />\n佢係我細路 <br />\n但佢又要叫我外公 <br />\n<br />\n我係我老婆個老公 <br />\n但係我老婆係我後媽個阿媽喎 <br />\n所以我係自己既外公 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到左新年 <br />\n黎料啦 <br />\n<br />\n我就同我後媽同我老豆 <br />\n即係同我繼女同女婿交換利是 <br />\n<br />\n我封廿蚊比我個仔 <br />\n佢話:「多謝老豆!」 <br />\n我又答返佢:「唔洗、舅父!係呢，咁我果封呢?」 <br />\n「你都痴線，我結左婚啦咩?」唉，我自己都亂左... <br />\n<br />\n食團年飯果陣 <br />\n我係抬面上面放左一封一千蚊利是<br />\n再拎返封利是上手 <br />\n叫左聲 :「多謝外公!」 <br />\n<br />\n好彩唔係街姐 <br />\n唔係真係比人捉去青山訓一排 <br />\n而家諗返自己真係痴痴地線 <br />\n自己比錢自己洗 <br />\n咪即係去自己鋪頭買野..."},{"pid":"fb530952caed2f1e9a17faada893363150fe9832","tid":95193,"uid":4586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T00:30:51.000Z","msg":"做咩姐你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f666dacf0a7b9c26e11e9513fed403ad92e88cf3","tid":95193,"uid":31837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T00:32:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做咩姐你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n新會員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"969188a51bfa84857da9cbc34d48104f49ef8068","tid":95193,"uid":78349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T00:37:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做咩姐你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29e7dfb781510998674dcfc1e1f5a13333492db9","tid":95193,"uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T01:21:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c658b45e33b96e5bf09136dbc205c311c002e44","tid":95193,"uid":21255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T01:46:17.000Z","msg":"又撚鳩啲新會然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}